            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Neptuno <lb n="2"/><expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>edem</abbr></expan> cum <lb n="3"/>signo <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Paternus <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>arc</abbr><ex>hitectus</ex></expan> et Aeli<lb break="no" n="6"/>us Macer ex <lb n="7"/>voto <expan><abbr>pos</abbr><ex>uerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ursprünglicher Standort auf dem mittleren Brückenpfeiler der römischen Neckarbrücke vermutlich in einer Ädikula. Material: gelber Keupersandstein.</p>
            </div>
